title: Facebook Experience - Story by ex-Facebook Software Engineer
description: If you've got a chance to meet a Facebook engineer, what would you ask?
body:
If you've got a chance to meet a Facebook engineer, what would you ask? Aizat Faiz was previously a Software Engineer at Facebook from 2010-2016. Worked on Growth at Facebook to increase the Monthly Active Users from 400 million to 2 billion Monthly Active Users.

[Ticket](https://appclub-facebookexperience.eventbrite.com)    [Recording](https://www.facebook.com/1803989609841203/videos/342096379889113/)
